divs: sighting detailswitness was passenger in vehicle traveling west on i-40 near the cornwell exitdirectly before the garth brooks blvd exit. witness glanced out the windown andsaw cigar shaped object that was silver\gray somewhat dulled color in sky. atfirst thought it was a plane. upon continued watching object, it did not move.witness was in heavy traffic and traffic was moving slowly. object appeared tonot move for apx time frame of 10 minutes. witness lost sight of object whentraffic picked up and road curve where witness could not see the same location.witness never saw object move or disappear.
